<span class="MsgBodyText"><b>Originally posted by:</b> thomas.x.hughes.jpmorgan.com<br />
<br />
So a typical domain class would look something like this :<br />
<br />
class Person <br />
{<br />
<br />
  private WritableValue name;<br />
  private WritableList relations;<br />
<br />
  String getName() <br />
  {<br />
    return (String) name.getValue();<br />
  }<br />
<br />
  List getRelations() <br />
  {<br />
    return new ArrayList(relations);<br />
  }<br />
<br />
  void addNameListener(IValueChangeListener l) <br />
  {<br />
    name.addValueChangeListener(l);<br />
  }<br />
<br />
  void addRelationsListener(IListChangeListener l) <br />
  {<br />
    relations.addListChangeListener(l);<br />
  }<br />
<br />
}<br />
<br />
?<br />
<br />
thanks, Tom</span>


